dataset_info.name: C++ Spaghetti Code Detection Dataset
dataset_info.description: Dataset containing clean C++ code paired with spaghettified versions using realistic compiler warnings and code quality issues

severity_levels.1: Critical - uninitialized vars, null deref, assignment as condition, out-of-bounds, use-after-free
severity_levels.2: High - signed/unsigned comparison, arithmetic overflow, switch fallthrough, division by zero, return local reference
severity_levels.3: Medium - unused vars/functions/params, missing return, misleading indentation, shadowing, infinite loops
